\b Neil Patrick Harris
\b0  (#93) & 
\b Shannen Doherty
\b0  (#96): Dammit, I hate being in the position of defending Shannen Doherty. I get that Neil Patrick is a vote for "Doogie Howser MD" and a vote for Shannen was a nod to "90210". That said, you have to put Shannen higher on the list than Neil. I don't mean 50 spots higher, but higher -- even if it's just on spot. "90210" was incredibly influential reinventing the teen angst format and was around for 10 years (albiet probably 2 or 3 years too long). "Doogie Howser" was... ah... kind of a stupid show with a lot of nerdy kids on it.\
